### ===========================
### 聊天接口 ChatController
### ===========================

### 普通聊天（阻塞式）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "你好，介绍一下 Spring AI 的核心功能",
  "conversationId": null,
  "model": null,
  "temperature": 0.7,
  "maxTokens": 1000
}

### 普通聊天 - 带指定模型
POST http://localhost:8080/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "帮我解释一下什么是 RAG",
  "conversationId": "test-conv-001",
  "model": "deepseek-chat",
  "temperature": 0.5,
  "maxTokens": 2000
}

### 流式聊天（SSE）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/chat/stream
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: text/event-stream

{
  "message": "用 Java 写一个快速排序算法",
  "conversationId": null,
  "temperature": 0.3,
  "maxTokens": 2000
}

### 清空对话历史
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/chat/test-conv-001

### ===========================
### RAG 检索接口 RagController
### ===========================

### 知识库检索
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rag/search?query=逾期处理&type=规则&topK=5

### 知识库检索 - 不指定类型
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rag/search?query=贷款利率计算&topK=3

### 混合检索
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rag/hybrid-search?query=M1阶段的征信上报&topK=5

### 重排序检索
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rag/rerank-search?query=客户逾期了怎么办&topK=5

### 智能 RAG 管道检索
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rag/pipeline?query=客户逾期了怎么办&topK=5

### 智能 RAG 管道检索 - 带对话ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rag/pipeline?query=还款方式有哪些&conversationId=test-conv-001&topK=3

### RAG 系统评估
POST http://localhost:8080/api/rag/evaluate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "逾期处理流程",
  "relevantDocIds": ["doc-001", "doc-002", "doc-003"],
  "topK": 5,
  "minTargetRecall": 0.8,
  "minTargetPrecision": 0.75
}

### ===========================
### 聊天调试接口 ChatDebugController
### ===========================

### 测试检索相似度
GET http://localhost:8080/api/chat/debug/test-search?query=逾期催收&includeContent=true

### 测试检索相似度 - 不含内容
GET http://localhost:8080/api/chat/debug/test-search?query=贷款审批流程&includeContent=false

### 向量库状态
GET http://localhost:8080/api/chat/debug/vector-store

### 查询扩展调试
GET http://localhost:8080/api/chat/debug/query-expansion?query=逾期了怎么办

### 查询重写调试
GET http://localhost:8080/api/chat/debug/query-rewrite?query=怎么还款&conversationId=test-conv-001

### 查询重写调试 - 无对话上下文
GET http://localhost:8080/api/chat/debug/query-rewrite?query=利率是多少

### ===========================
### 提示词管理 PromptController
### ===========================

### 获取 System 提示词
GET http://localhost:8080/api/prompts/system

### 获取 RAG QA 提示词
GET http://localhost:8080/api/prompts/rag/qa

### 获取 Function Calling 提示词
GET http://localhost:8080/api/prompts/function/calling

### 获取提示词状态
GET http://localhost:8080/api/prompts/status

### 创建 Prompt 草稿版本
POST http://localhost:8080/api/prompts/registry/drafts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "promptKey": "system-prompt",
  "env": "dev",
  "content": "你是一个专业的贷款助手，帮助用户解答贷款相关问题。请用简洁专业的语言回答。",
  "variablesJson": "{\"maxTokens\": 2000}",
  "modelScope": "deepseek-chat",
  "operator": "debug-user"
}

### 发布 Prompt 版本
POST http://localhost:8080/api/prompts/registry/publish
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "promptKey": "system-prompt",
  "env": "dev",
  "version": 1,
  "operator": "debug-user",
  "remark": "首次发布系统提示词"
}

### 回滚 Prompt 版本
POST http://localhost:8080/api/prompts/registry/rollback
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "promptKey": "system-prompt",
  "env": "dev",
  "version": 1,
  "operator": "debug-user",
  "remark": "回滚到v1版本"
}

### 查询当前生效 Prompt
GET http://localhost:8080/api/prompts/registry/active?promptKey=system-prompt&env=dev

### 查询 Prompt 历史版本
GET http://localhost:8080/api/prompts/registry/versions?promptKey=system-prompt&env=dev

### ===========================
### 成本统计 AiCostController
### ===========================

### 今日成本统计
GET http://localhost:8080/api/cost/today

### 本周成本统计
GET http://localhost:8080/api/cost/week

### 本月成本统计
GET http://localhost:8080/api/cost/month

### 指定时间范围成本统计
GET http://localhost:8080/api/cost/range?start=2026-05-01T00:00:00&end=2026-05-12T23:59:59

### ===========================
### 健康检查 HealthController
### ===========================

### 健康检查
GET http://localhost:8080/health
